---
layout: base.njk
title: Related Groups — PoliTechs.uk
description: We're part of a wider ecosystem of organisations working at the intersection of politics, technology, and society.
---

<main class="page-main">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Related Groups</h1>
    <p class="page-intro">
      We're part of a wider ecosystem of organisations working at the intersection of politics, technology,
      and society. Here are some groups we admire and collaborate with.
    </p>
    <div class="row g-4">
      {% for group in groups %}
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card group-card h-100">
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <h5 class="card-title">{{ group.name }}</h5>
            <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">{{ group.description }}</p>
            <div class="group-tags mb-3">
              {% for tag in group.tags %}
              <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-secondary me-1">{{ tag }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            <a href="{{ group.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline-primary align-self-start">
              Visit website &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
